    <font size="+1"><b>Semi Automatic Agent Job Application Pipeline
        using Hermes</b></font><br>
    by Marc Gloor <br>
    <hr width="100%">
    <p><b><img src="data/hermes-job-pipeline.png"
          alt="hermes-job-pipeline.gif" height="443" width="788"><br>
