        Produce 300 or more job applications in a month with just an
        hour daily work<br>
      </b> </p>
    <p data-start="64" data-end="462">My newly developed semi-automated
      pipeline leverages a single <a
        href="https://hermes-agent.nousresearch.com">Hermes</a> AI agent
      to fundamentally shift the job application workflow. Feeding a job
      URL into the system prompts the agent to extract the necessary
      requirements, compile a custom LaTeX resume plus a signed cover
      letter, and handle the tedious task of filling out ATS HR forms
      over and over again with the same crap.<br>
      <br>
      This approach completely bypasses the traditional bottleneck of a
      few high-quality manual applications per month. By automating the
      heavy lifting and relying on a human-in-the-loop solely for
      CAPTCHA verification to overcome bot walls.<b><br>
        <br>
      </b>
      <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;
        charset=windows-1252">
      <b> The resulting efficiency yields a substantially higher rate of
        interview invitations and resulting number of interviews higher
        than your competing non-agentic peer group.</b><br>
      <br>
      Organization is built-in: every application is neatly filed into a
      timestamped directory containing the URL, CV, and cover letter.
      With a <b>processing time of ~5–8 minutes per application</b>,
      the system operates completely asynchronously alongside other
      tasks. A polished version of the project is slated for future
      publication on GitLab.<br>
      <br>
      I can assist you to build your very own tailored hermes
      application engine, just get in touch with me.<br>
      <br>
      <b>Tech Stack / Requirements:</b><br>
      Linux Desktop or Windows<br>
      Hermes Agent v0.16.0 (2026.6.5) or higher<br>
      Model: gpt-5.4 or equivalent agentic tool capacity<br>
    </p>
